  "text": "As Table I shows, the highest reported throughput for a hardware implementation for the GF(64) (192,96) code is 3.8 Mbit/s at an SNR of 2.4 dB [CITATION_1] using EMS with the Bubble Check algorithm. We note that, in this case, AMSA presents a significant improvement in throughput.",
